## ğŸš€ Quick Start for Contributors

### Find Your First Task
1. Check [GitHub Issues](https://github.com/YOUR_ORG/drophub/issues) labeled `good-first-issue`
2. Join our [Discord Community](https://discord.gg/drophub)
3. Read [CONTRIBUTING.md](CONTRIBUTING.md)

### Development Workflow
```bash
# Create feature branch
git checkout -b feature/your-feature-name

# Make changes and test
npm test

# Commit with conventional commits
git commit -m "feat: add product bulk import"

# Push and create PR
git push origin feature/your-feature-name
```

